हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Dhokha On The Wedding Day” ek emotional thriller hai jahan misunderstanding, jealousy aur greed ban jaate hain ek pregnant aurat ke dard bhare nightmare ki wajah. Raj Diwan apni pregnant bhabhi Sonia ke saath airport se ghar laut raha hota hai… lekin ek chhupi hui aankh ne unki rishtedari ko kuch aur hi samajh liya.Tanya, Raj ki hone wali dulhan, ek gandi chaal chalti hai. Uski possessiveness aur insecurity ban jaati hai Sonia ke liye ek torture tale ki shuruaat. Shaadi se pehle, dosti, vishwas aur insaaniyat ka asli chehra sabke saamne aata hai—aur ek qeemti 250 crore ka pendant ban jaata hai confusion aur badla ka symbol. Abhi dekhana shuru karein.
